  "industry_note": "UNS S30400 / SUS304 / 1.4301 — 가장 흔한 18-8 austenitic stainless. max service 870°C intermittent. 425-870°C sensitization 우려 (Cr23C6 입계석출). 식품·의료·건축·반도체 piping 표준. Austenitic → Q+T 불가 . 의도된 variant: Annealed / Aged / SH / Cast.",
